NAME
    Bundle::Perl::Critic - A CPAN bundle for Perl::Critic and related
    modules

SYNOPSIS
      perl -MCPAN -e 'install Bundle::Perl::Critic'

DESCRIPTION
    This is a CPAN bundle file for installing Perl::Critic,
    Test::Perl::Critic, <criticism> and several Policy plugin modules, along
    with all their dependencies.

CONTENTS
        Perl::Critic

        Test::Perl::Critic

        Perl::Critic::More

        Perl::Critic::Bangs

        Perl::Critic::Lax

        criticism

